This was all run with the v1.0.0 sysimage install of FUSE on perlmutter.

First go interactive:
  salloc --nodes 1 --qos interactive --time 4:00:00 --constraint cpu --account=mp94 --ntasks=1 --cpus-per-task=128

Run:
  module use /global/common/software/m3739/perlmutter/fuse/modules
  module load fuse/v1.0.0.lua
  srun --cpu-bind=none fuse run_hdb5.jl

Plot (I copied the .csv files locally)
  julia> using FUSE, Plots
  julia> sty = FUSE.load_HDB5_validation("HDB5_validation_2026-03-10T16-29-56.csv");
  julia> plot(sty)


N.B.: Result can otherwise be reproduced by instantiating the Manifest.toml
        included here in julia v1.11.7